title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Beechcraft 17 - using the navigation system
description:
In this video we will have a look at how to use the navigation system from the Beechcraft 17 Staggerwing. The system available in this aircraft is pretty limited but it is still very useful to use for navigation purposes.
